- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper focuses on sorting algorithms and their performance guarantees. 
- cs.PF (Performance) is another possible category as the paper evaluates the performance of the algorithms on large machines and varying input sizes. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is a possible category as the paper involves the analysis of algorithms and their asymptotic performance. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the complexity of the sorting algorithms and their performance guarantees.
